{"tid":1228684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔叻摺花既巴絲打可以入黎睇下","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:44:16.000Z","uid":227229,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ffee84a2792cefeb0e241462fca0fe537e3a6528","tid":1228684,"uid":227229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，我第一次開post。<br />\n<br />\n我見大家都摺紙鶴同玫瑰。因為我剪剪貼貼比較叻啲，同埋睇到巴絲打話可以用菊花，所以就上網學，用咗張白畫紙整咗朵菊花。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEuESBV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEuESBV.png&h=619c8578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得個size 大少少會好啲。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有啲醜，但我都想出少少力，希望果位烈士可以安息、一路好走。<br />\n<br />\n摺紙教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nAOjxkRHOn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnAOjxkRHOn4&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe26Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=7fc167b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nAOjxkRHOn4</a><br />\n<br />\n各位 辛苦晒啦！"}]}